                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Badmorda wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">I have seen lately several folks talk about Vanguard as something they are really looking forward to. I was curious what it was about that game that seems more interesting than EQ2 or WoW. Is it who is making the game? Or are there features that you all find intrigueing?
