<br />

<br />
The only solid thing that can be said is what has been said by the few people that have actually seen the game itself.
<br />

<br />
Woody of gucomics.com fame has been to the Vanguard HQ twice that we know of and has made some very favorable comments on it.  Better todate than he's said about anything else.
<br />

<br />
The summary can be said this way.  Vanguard is using an actual design document i.e. "The Vision".  This is the thing that Brenlo and crew have been talking about making these last 30 somedays and the reason oh so many Enchanters have either parked thier toons in favor of another class, or deleted their accounts (obviously if Brenlo and crew are only now after 3 years of the Verant gang being gone making class definitions of their own, then for the last three years they've just been winging it....and it shows).
<br />

<br />
The second thing that can be said is that according to Woody who of anyone is more critical of art than most, Vanguard has the best graphics of anything either out or on the planning board that he's seen.
<br />

<br />
My best suggestion is go to the gucomics.com forums and do a search for Vanguard and read what he has to say.  Better when ever possible to get the words from the original source than anyone paraprasing after all.
<br />

<br />
Hope that helps you.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />**************************************
