<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
And you see to be confusing the world with the vision.  The vision was about crap like "Sorry, melee will require other people to bind them" and "Sitting on boats for half an hour unable to do anything, not even fish"  or perhaps the oh-so-popular "kiss your gear goodbye if you die in a dangerous place because your body rots in 24 hours and there's no way to get it back"  (which admittedly they did fix, but that was the "vision" of the game at release).  The vision was always about mechanics. NEVER was the vision referenced in the context of lore, or RP.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
